		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wouldn't dare to call myself &quot;talented&quot;, but a few things that <em>might</em> help:<br /><br />- Rewrite in major (or lydian or mixolydian) instead of minor <br />- Retime into some other time signature other than 4/4<br />- Make it a little faster<br />- Swing the 8th notes<br />- Add grace notes<br />- Outline chords instead of using arpeggios<br />- Consider more use of pizzicato; don't be afraid to have brief moments of silence

		

		</td>
